    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "Q9mzu",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": 13000,
      "name": "Meet Armenia 02 Opportunity",
      "clip": true,
      "width": 1600,
      "height": 900,
      "fill": "$brand-dark",
      "layout": "none",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "kTUAn",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 80,
          "name": "s2title",
          "fill": "$brand-white",
          "content": "1. The Opportunity",
          "fontFamily": "$sans",
          "fontSize": 56,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "p5MFt",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 170,
          "name": "s2body",
          "fill": "$brand-white",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 1408,
          "content": "Armenia is entering a new visibility window.\n\nTourism is growing. Direct access from London is launching. Smaller, less obvious destinations are gaining global attention. Armenia is moving closer to Europe through the EU visa liberalisation process.\n\nThe timing is right for Armenia to become more than a place people discover by accident.\n\nIt can become a country people feel connected to before they travel.",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "$sans",
          "fontSize": 26
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "YuhDn",
          "x": 640,
          "y": 500,
          "name": "s2center",
          "width": 320,
          "height": 180,
          "fill": "$brand-red",
