    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "jODwr",
      "x": 15480,
      "y": 13000,
      "name": "Meet Armenia 10 Recommendation",
      "clip": true,
      "width": 1600,
      "height": 900,
      "fill": "$brand-dark",
      "layout": "none",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "t1U5N",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 70,
          "name": "s10title",
          "fill": "$brand-white",
          "content": "9. The Recommendation Layer",
          "fontFamily": "$sans",
          "fontSize": 52,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "rK022",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 160,
          "name": "s10text",
          "fill": "$brand-white",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 1408,
          "content": "From content to personal routes.\n\nAs people interact with the content, the system learns what kind of Armenia they are drawn to.\n\nThey may become:\n- a wine person\n- a mountain person\n- a food person\n- a history person\n- a hidden places person\n- a family trip person\n- a city weekend person\n- a slow travel person\n\nThis creates the bridge from media to product.\n\nExample:\nYou met Armenian wine, duduk, and mountain villages.\nHere is your 4-day Armenia route.\n\nContent becomes a signal.\nSignals become preferences.\nPreferences become routes.\nRoutes become trips.",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "fontFamily": "$sans",
          "fontSize": 22
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "Fm7dJ",
          "x": 96,
