    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "l35RPN",
      "x": 25800,
      "y": 13000,
      "name": "Meet Armenia 16 Vision",
      "clip": true,
      "width": 1600,
      "height": 900,
      "fill": "$brand-dark",
      "layout": "none",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "w11y9",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 70,
          "name": "s16title",
          "fill": "$brand-white",
          "content": "15. The Vision",
          "fontFamily": "$sans",
          "fontSize": 52,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Z9MZ80",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 160,
          "name": "s16text",
          "fill": "$brand-white",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 1408,
          "content": "A new way to meet countries.\n\nMeet Armenia is the first chapter of a new travel media model:\n\ncountries as characters\nculture as interface\ncontent as the beginning of a journey\n\nToday:\nArmenia as a character-based media brand.\n\nNext:\nPersonalized Armenia routes.\n\nLater:\nA platform for meeting countries, regions, and cultures through character-led storytelling.\n\nFinal line:\n\nFirst you meet Armenia.\n\nThen you go.",
          "lineHeight": 1.25,
          "fontFamily": "$sans",
          "fontSize": 25
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "ptWNo",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 780,
          "name": "s16final",
          "fill": "$brand-yellow",
          "content": "Meet Armenia · First you meet Armenia. Then you go.",
          "fontFamily": "$serif-italic",
          "fontSize": 44,
          "fontWeight": "normal",
          "fontStyle": "italic"
        }
      ]
